headline: Baxter to Present at 7th Annual Evercore HealthCONx Conference
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., November 19, 2024--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, will present at the 7th Annual Evercore HealthCONx Conference on Thursday, December 5, 2024. Joel Grade, Baxter’s chief financial officer, is scheduled to present at 9:10 a.m. Eastern Time.
